                  <h4 class="outline-header">2.3.7 Nombres comparativos</h4>
                 <p>
                  <br>¶Los nombres comparatios
                  de esta lengua 
                    se 
                     for<br>man 
                  de esta manera. 
                  v.g. 
                  Toman el positivo, y añaden
                  <br>le una sílaba ante o pos. 
                  Y 
                    así dicen, 
                  <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">huazáca Pe-<br>dro, huazácati 
                     Juan</mark><span class="content hide inline"></span></span>. 
                  Bueno es 
                    Pedro, pero un poco
                  <br>mejor es Juan. 
                    l. 
                    <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">céläci huazäca Iuan</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>céláci huazáca Iuan</caption><tr><td>cé-</td><td>láci</td><td>hua</td><td>záca</td><td>Iuan</td></tr><tr><td>another(pre-QUANT)</td><td>small.amount</td><td>PRF</td><td>be.good</td><td>Juan</td></tr><td colspan="5">'John is a little bit better.'</td></table></span></span>. 
                    l. 
                    <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">tijca huazá<br>ca Iuan</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>tijca huazáca Iuan</caption><tr><td>ti</td><td>=ca</td><td>hua</td><td>záca</td><td>Iuan</td></tr><tr><td>exist</td><td>=EMPH</td><td>PRF</td><td>be.good</td><td>Juan</td></tr><td colspan="5">'It really is (the case that) Juan is good.'</td></table></span></span>. 
                    l. 
                    <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">tijca titéte Iuan</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>tijcatitéte Iuan</caption><tr><td>ti</td><td>=ca</td><td>=ti</td><td>=téte</td><td>Iuan</td></tr><tr><td>exist</td><td>=EMPH</td><td>=PT</td><td>=very</td><td>Juan</td></tr><td colspan="5">'Juan really is [good?]'</td></table></span></span>, 
                    <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">huagátici quîchitij</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>huagátici quíchitij</caption><tr><td>hua</td><td>gáti</td><td>=ci</td><td>quíchi</td><td>=ti</td></tr><tr><td>PRF</td><td>white</td><td>=only</td><td>paper</td><td>=this</td></tr><td colspan="5">'This paper is only white.'</td></table></span></span>, 
